OL,3,CRescue operation ongoing after boat
OL,4,Csinks in Carlingford Lough
OL,6,FA rescue operation is under way after
OL,7,Fa fishing boat with two people on
OL,8,Fboard sank in Carlingford Lough on
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,11,FThe Department of Transport said the
OL,12,FCoast Guard received a report the
OL,13,Fvessel was in trouble near Greencastle
OL,14,FPoint, Co Down, shortly after 12.30pm.
OL,16,FOne person was recovered from the
OL,17,Fvessel by a local boat and transferred
OL,18,Fto the care of paramedics at Greenore
OL,19,Fharbour.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
