OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780517152
OL,3,CRescue operation ongoing after boat
OL,4,Csinks in Carlingford Lough
OL,6,FA search was ongoing to recover a
OL,7,Fsecond person.
OL,9,FAn RNLI lifeboat from Kilkeel and the
OL,10,FGreenore Irish Coast Guard boat were
OL,11,Fsent, along with Coastguard rescue
OL,12,Fteams from Newcastle and Kilkeel.
OL,14,FThe Irish Coast Guard's Rescue 116
OL,15,Fhelicopter took part in the search and
OL,16,Fa Royal Navy helicopter assisted.
OL,18,FGardai said they were also on the
OL,19,Fscene.
